                    <span>This book just shows how spectacular a desert can look with the magnificent photos around the Mojave desert and Death valley of emptiness, stark flowers and blooms and just superb landscapes. It'll give you some inspiration to find something to look for even in a desert. <p>I know I will as I will be going to Ayer's Rock (Uluru) in Australia in a few months and it's also a big desert!</span>
                  
